OL,3,CJury sent out to consider findings in
OL,4,CNoah Donohoe inquest
OL,6,FThe jury in the inquest into the death
OL,7,Fof Belfast schoolboy Noah Donohoe has
OL,8,Fbeen sent out to consider its findings.
OL,10,FThe 14-year-old was found naked in a
OL,11,Fstorm drain in the city in June 2020
OL,12,Fafter being missing for six days.
OL,14,FThe jury of eight men and two women
OL,15,Fhas been tasked with unanimously
OL,16,Fagreeing responses to 10 questions,
OL,17,Fincluding the date of Noah's death and
OL,18,Fwhether any errors made by police
OL,19,Fcontributed to his death.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/5
