OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1782907570
OL,3,CJury sent out to consider findings in
OL,4,CNoah Donohoe inquest
OL,6,FIt comes after almost six months of
OL,7,Fevidence at Belfast Coroner's Court
OL,8,Finvolving 76 witnesses, statements
OL,9,Ffrom a further 42 people, maps, video
OL,10,Ffootage, photographs, police logs and
OL,11,Fexpert reports.
OL,13,FNoah, a pupil at St Malachy's College,
OL,14,Fwas found in the storm drain tunnel in
OL,15,Fnorth Belfast six days after he left
OL,16,Fhome on his bike to meet two friends
OL,17,Fin the Cavehill area of the city.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
