PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1782907570
OL,3,CJury sent out to consider findings in
OL,4,CNoah Donohoe inquest
OL,6,FCCTV evidence and witnesses show Noah
OL,7,Ftook a detour from his planned route,
OL,8,Fcycling instead along York Road and
OL,9,Fending up on Northwood Road where it
OL,10,Fis suggested he entered the tunnel via
OL,11,Fa culvert behind a house.
OL,13,FThe inquest was shown CCTV of Noah
OL,14,Fcycling naked along Northwood Road,
OL,15,Fand evidence that some residents heard
OL,16,Fnoises including screams on the night
OL,17,Fof June 21 when he went missing.
OL,19,FA post-mortem examination found the
OL,20,Fcause of death was drowning.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/5
