PN,41704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1782907570
OL,3,CJury sent out to consider findings in
OL,4,CNoah Donohoe inquest
OL,6,FThe jury is charged with reaching
OL,7,Ffindings including how Noah came by
OL,8,Fhis death.
OL,10,FCoroner Mr Justice Rooney took two
OL,11,Fdays to read his charge to the jury
OL,12,Fwhich numbered more than 70,000 words.
OL,14,FHe told the jury it "must decide the
OL,15,Fcase solely on the evidence you have
OL,16,Fseen and heard in this court, rather
OL,17,Fthan guesswork or any rumours you may
OL,18,Fhave heard".
